                                                                                                                        【只要有耐心，<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%89%AB%E5%B8%9A%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%A9%E9%83%BD%E8%83%BD%E7%AB%8B%23&amp;from=default">#扫帚天天都能立#</a>！】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23NASA%E7%AB%8B%E6%89%AB%E6%8A%8A%E6%8C%91%E6%88%98%23&amp;from=default">#NASA立扫把挑战#</a>刷屏网络，网传“NASA称因地球重力角度特殊，所以扫帚能够站起来。”然而真相是，扫帚能立起来与今天的引力无关，只要有耐心扫帚每天都可以立！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0%23&amp;from=default">#隔离日记#</a>，你家的扫帚能立起来吗？<img class="W_img_face" render="ext" src="//img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a1/2018new_doge02_org.png" title="[doge]" alt="[doge]" type="face" style="visibility: hidden;">网友：我唯一立不起来的就是flag<img class="W_img_face" render="ext" src="//img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/83/2018new_kuxiao_org.png" title="[允悲]" alt="[允悲]" type="face" style="visibility: hidden;">（图据网友） ​​​​                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【教育部：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%BC%BA%E8%A1%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8A%E7%BD%91%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1%23&amp;from=default">#不得强行让学生每天上网打卡#</a>】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%BC%BA%E8%A1%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%95%99%E5%B8%88%E5%BD%95%E6%92%AD%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%BB%E5%88%B6%E6%AD%A2%23&amp;from=default">#强行要求所有教师录播课程须制止#</a>近期，部分地方陆续开始了网上“停课不停学”工作，教育部有关负责人回应，对小学低年级上网学习不作统一硬性要求，由家长和学生自愿选择，对其他学段学生作出限时限量的具体规定，避免学生网上学习时间过长。同时，不得强行 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItKAAkyBO" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470906044899600:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470906044899600&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <!-- 时间 -->

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【中央赴湖北指导组：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%AE%81%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%A9%E5%BA%8A%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%BA%E7%AD%89%E5%BA%8A%23&amp;from=default">#宁可让床等人不要让人等床#</a>】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%BA%94%E6%94%B6%E5%B0%BD%E6%94%B6+%E5%88%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E7%BC%93%23&amp;from=default">#应收尽收 刻不容缓#</a>11日上午，中共中央政治局委员、国务院副总理孙春兰率中央指导组实地了解应收尽收落实情况。孙春兰察看了为患者准备的生活用品和医疗设施，详细询问收治及生活保障等准备情况。她强调，要坚定不移落实应收尽收，加快增设床位并提 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItK2F3uTk" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470885010833734:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470885010833734&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【工信部：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%B8%AE%E6%89%B6%E5%8A%9B%E5%BA%A6%23&amp;from=default">#加大对中小企业帮扶力度#</a>】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>，11日，工信部召开企业复工复产电视电话会议指出，疫情发生以来，中小企业受疫情的影响最大，支持中小企业发展，对于稳定社会预期、缓解社会焦虑具有重要作用。会议要求加大对中小企业的资金支持等政策措施，加大对中小企业的帮扶力度。研究制 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItK0e0MzF" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470883500186723:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470883500186723&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609332442&amp;ssig=2DJot%2FqaYq" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>

        <div class="WB_detail">
                            <div class="WB_info">
                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4470877372583659" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/ItJQlaQ7V?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-11 20:21" date="1581423693000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4470877372583659:fromprofile"> 2月11日 20:21</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【人民网评：疫情面前，白衣天使化身最坚强的战士】“病毒扼住了生命的咽喉，但它决不能使我们屈服”。穿上那身厚重的、憋闷的防护服，白衣天使就是病毒的“狙击手”、患者的“生命线”。这数万名在前线的医务工作者就是我们决战决胜的底气所在！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%91%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%A0%23&amp;from=default">#你守护大家我守护你#</a>，待到春暖花开、疫情散去，希望他 ​​​​...<a href="javascript:void(0);" action-type="widget_photoview" action-data="uid=2286908003&amp;mid=4470877372583659&amp;pid=884f7263ly1gbspyedzc1j20go0gomzd" suda-uatrack="key=tblog_fstt&amp;value=pop_butt_home" imagecard="pid=884f7263ly1gbspyedzc1j20go0gomzd"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_img">¡</i>查看图片</a><a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItJQlaQ7V" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470877372583659:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470877372583659&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【国务院：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8F%AF%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%81%E7%94%A8%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E5%91%A8%E8%BE%B9%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%8C%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%23&amp;from=default">#可依法征用医院周边酒店作为医务人员休息场所#</a>】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%91%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%A0%23&amp;from=default">#你守护大家我守护你#</a>国务院办公厅今日发布《关于改善一线医务人员工作条件切实关心医务人员身心健康的若干措施》。其中明确，县级以上地方人民政府可依法征用医院周边酒店作为医务人员休息场所，以满足一线医务人员单人单间休息条件，并对基 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItJKYrvX4" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470874046557682:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470874046557682&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【教育部、财政部：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8A%A9%E5%AD%A6%E8%B4%B7%E6%AC%BE%E5%8F%97%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%BB%B6%E6%9C%9F%E8%BF%98%E6%AC%BE%23&amp;from=default">#助学贷款受疫情影响可延期还款#</a>】日前，教育部、财政部联合印发通知，要求积极资助患病家庭经济困难学生，在疫情防控期间因受疫情影响不能正常还本付息的国家助学贷款借款学生，按照相关规定可合理延后还款期限。如因患新型冠状病毒感染肺炎失去还款能力，要协调经办银行启动救助机 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItJiMCEtz" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470856569212057:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470856569212057&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【中央赴湖北指导组约谈武汉市副市长等3人 “要向这些患者挨个赔礼道歉”】“应收尽收是防控新冠肺炎疫情的关键，要把好事办好，怎么能把好事办坏？这些负责转运危重和重症病人的党员干部为什么不跟车？现在的武汉就是战时状态，这些人的行为十分恶劣。”<br>10日晚，在中央赴湖北指导组约谈会上，国务院 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItJcftEt2" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470852517067072:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470852517067072&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                <a name="4470848155434796" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/ItJ5dmNQ0?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-11 18:25" date="1581416727000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4470848155434796:fromprofile"> 2月11日 18:25</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【最高检发布<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%AA%E5%A6%A8%E5%AE%B3%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%23&amp;from=default">#首批十个妨害疫情防控犯罪典型案例#</a><img class="W_img_face" render="ext" src="//img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/48/2018new_huatong_org.png" title="[话筒]" alt="[话筒]" type="face" style="visibility: hidden;">】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%B3%E5%8A%9E%E7%90%86%E5%A6%A8%E5%AE%B3%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6363%E4%BB%B6%23&amp;from=default">#全国检察机关办理妨害疫情防控案件363件#</a>2月11日，最高人民检察院对外发布首批十个妨害新冠肺炎疫情防控犯罪典型案例，共涉及抗拒疫情防控措施、暴力伤医、制假售假、哄抬物价、破坏野生动物资源等七类犯罪。具体案例↓↓<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;截至2月7日 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItJ5dmNQ0" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470848155434796:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470848155434796&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【好消息！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%AE%81%E5%A4%8F%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E7%8E%87%E8%BE%BE41.5%25%23&amp;from=default">#宁夏治愈率达41.5%#</a>：累计治愈22人】11日下午，经宁夏新型冠状病毒肺炎诊疗组精心治疗，宁夏8名新冠肺炎确诊患者正式解除隔离，治愈出院，其中年龄最大的患者76岁，最小的11岁。目前，宁夏共有22名确诊患者出院，治愈率达到41.5%。<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%BD%91-%E5%AE%81%E5%A4%8F%E9%A2%91%E9%81%93?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=人民网-宁夏频道">@人民网-宁夏频道</a> <a title="2月11日，宁夏又有8例确诊患者治愈出院" href="http://t.cn/A6hwUTZ2" alt="http://t.cn/A6hwUTZ2" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_link">O</i>2月11日，宁夏又有8例确诊患者治愈出院</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【戳图了解！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E9%A3%9F%E5%A0%82%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%98%B2%E8%8C%83%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#单位食堂如何防范疫情#</a>】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>，单位食堂环境下如何防范新冠肺炎？牢记以下这六点：①保持环境清洁，公共接触物品及时清洁消毒；②经常开窗换气，保持空气流通；③保持食物加工间清洁干燥、及时清理厨余垃圾；④工作人员戴口罩、穿工服，做好防护；⑤勤洗手；⑥加强对食堂工 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItIYzodow" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470844035771364:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470844035771364&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                <a name="4470842421363809" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/ItIVY5IMV?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-11 18:02" date="1581415360000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4470842421363809:fromprofile"> 2月11日 18:02</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%B0%91%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%8F%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%23&amp;from=default">#民民小调查#</a>【你的口罩会重复用吗？】中国疾控中心流行病学首席专家吴尊友在回答网友提问时表示，有些人出门一次性戴七八个口罩，这完全没有必要。普通人一般一次性医用口罩一个就可以了，也没必要戴一次打电话喝口水后就马上扔掉，<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%8F%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%23&amp;from=default">#普通人口罩可重复使用#</a>。你的用几次才换呢？ <a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4470842421363809:1022-hudongvote:1022%3A2317162020_226386_-_566a0a" title="人民网的微博投票" href="https://vote.weibo.com/h5/index/index?vote_id=2020_226386_-_566a0a" alt="https://vote.weibo.com/h5/index/index?vote_id=2020_226386_-_566a0a" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_vote">R</i>人民网的微博投票</a> ​​​​                                            </div>
                                                                <div class="WB_expand_media_box " style="display: none;" node-type="feed_list_media_disp"></div>

                                                                                                                        【民政部：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E8%87%B4%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E7%9B%91%E6%8A%A4%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%8A%A5%23&amp;from=default">#疫情致儿童监护缺失第一时间上报#</a>】近日，民政部办公厅下发通知，要求做好因新冠肺炎疫情影响造成监护缺失的儿童救助保护工作。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;通知明确，各地要指导本地儿童督导员、儿童主任在乡镇（街道）、村（居）民委员会统一部署下，及时发现因新冠肺炎疫情影响造成监护缺失的儿童，包括父 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItIMHmlrS" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470836675325668:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470836675325668&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【小心"退改签""献爱心"！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E8%B0%A8%E9%98%B2%E4%B8%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E8%AF%88%E9%AA%97%23&amp;from=default">#谨防不法分子利用疫情诈骗#</a>】银保监会12日发布风险提示称，近期一些银行保险机构收到投诉反映，有不法分子利用疫情发布虚假信息实施诈骗，诈骗手法包括发送虚假“退改签”短信，窃取消费者银行卡号、密码、验证码等，转走卡内余额；以“采购防护物资”“献爱心”等为幌子发布 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItIJ8zXIG" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470834468571046:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470834468571046&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【人民日报刊登北大医师科普文章：普通人 三句话】疫情面前，我们不仅需要强大的医疗，更需要病人自身良好的免疫力。但病毒肆虐时，在短期内迅速提升免疫力很难，我们普通人，应该怎么办？三句话：加强防护，好好睡觉，平和心态。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>→<a title="正确认识 科学应对（开卷知新）" href="http://t.cn/A6hwbato" alt="http://t.cn/A6hwbato" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_link">O</i>正确认识 科学应对（开卷知新）</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【“一”起上！到火线去！为了这场生死较量】她，报告疫情一马当先；他，连夜请战守护一方平安；他，青春永远定格在抗疫一线……每一个平凡岗位，总有人无私奉献。到“战场”去！到“火线”去！当无数的“一”，汇聚成“万”。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>，我们一定会打赢这场战“疫”！戳，致敬这些幕后英雄→ ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItIuLqmEX" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470825556283635:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470825556283635&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【疾控专家：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%B2%A1%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%80%A7%E6%88%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%23&amp;from=default">#没必要一次性戴多个口罩#</a>】中国疾控中心流行病学首席专家吴尊友在回答网友提问时表示，有些人出门一次性戴七八个口罩，完全没有必要。普通人一般<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%80%A7%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%23&amp;from=default">#一次性医用口罩一个就可以#</a>了。而且没必要戴一次，打电话喝口水后就马上扔掉，<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%8F%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%23&amp;from=default">#普通人口罩可重复使用#</a>。<a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4470822678307597:1042163-video:1042163%3A4470822627377198:page_100206_home:2286908003:4470822678307597:2286908003" title="人民网的微博视频" href="http://t.cn/A6hwwYMV" alt="http://t.cn/A6hwwYMV" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>人民网的微博视频</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【外交部：中国有能力把疫情对经济影响降至最低】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>外交部发言人耿爽11日在回答新冠肺炎疫情对中国经济影响的相关提问时说，中国经济的基本面以及长期向好的趋势不会因为疫情而改变，我们有能力把疫情对经济的影响降至最低。他说，近日国际货币基金组织、世界银行等国际机构都表示，中 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItIndnpFR" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470820875580239:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470820875580239&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4470818904174414" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/ItIk2hvXg?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-11 16:29" date="1581409753000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4470818904174414:fromprofile"> 2月11日 16:29</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%86%85%E8%92%99%E5%8F%A4%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E4%B9%B3%E8%82%89%E5%88%B6%E5%93%81600%E5%90%A8%23&amp;from=default">#内蒙古支援湖北乳肉制品600吨#</a>今日启运】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>11日下午，一件件牛奶在呼和浩特市集装上车。内蒙古支援湖北省乳制品和肉制品等生活必需品今日启运。此次支援的物资包括：200吨羊肉、100吨牛肉、100吨猪肉和200吨牛奶。内蒙古自治区商务厅厅长田永告诉记者，这批物资由内蒙古自治区分别 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/ItIk2hvXg" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4470818904174414:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4470818904174414&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                              【教育部：<a target=\"_blank\" render=\"ext\" suda-uatrack=\"key=topic_click&value=click_topic\" class=\"a_topic\" extra-data=\"type=topic\" href=\"\/\/s.weibo.com\/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%BC%BA%E8%A1%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8A%E7%BD%91%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1%23&from=default\">#不得强行让学生每天上网打卡#<\/a>】<a
